1
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:30,000
[Sunshine of My Life]

2
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,700
[Episode 41]

3
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,000
President Tang, you have great taste indeed.

4
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:39,000
It is magnificent.

5
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,800
How many stories does this building have?

6
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:45,000
You didn't come here to look at the view, right?

7
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:52,330
It's like this.

8
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:58,800
I've received the lawyer's letter.

9
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:02,400
I came here today to specifically apologize to you.

10
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:05,200
I wasn't aware of this matter at all.

11
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:08,400
That Bai Xiaoman did this all behind my back.

12
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,900
If I had known, I would have stopped her.

13
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:11,800
Did you instigate it?

14
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:16,600
After all, didn't you do the same thing before?

15
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:22,200
I admit that back then when I first started managing the company,

16
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:24,400
I pulled some dirty tricks.

17
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,600
But my intention was to learn from the successful experiences of others.

18
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:30,200
I didn't cause any negative impact, right?

19
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:32,800
Please believe it when I say Bai Xiaoman and I are completely different.

20
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:35,400
I'm highly educated and I have a family inheritance.

21
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:39,200
I want to save face and I have professional ethics.

22
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:41,810
Let me say it like this.

23
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:46,800
When it comes to the fashion company, I have

24
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:50,000
no interest at all. I don't like it.

25
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,400
Bai Xiaoman promised me that she would

26
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,800
manage the company well on my behalf.

27
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:58,000
Being easily swayed, I said you can go manage it then.

28
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,800
Who knew she would create such a mess?

29
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:04,600
I must even personally come to clean up her mess.

30
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,400
President Tang,

31
00:03:12,770 --> 00:03:15,570
regardless of how big Haiyao has grown now,

32
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:20,500
it's something my father put in so much effort to build from the ground up.

33
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:23,600
I can't let it be ruined at the hand of a woman, right?

34
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:26,400
Both of our companies

35
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:29,800
are the biggest, most well-known brands in the country.

36
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,000
But times are difficult for everyone now.

37
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,600
We've been bullied by e-commerce to what state? You should know.

38
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:37,300
How many of our stores have closed down?

39
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:41,200
Under these circumstances, we should get through the difficulties together, right?

40
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,000
We can't tear each other down.

41
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:46,000
Look, it seems like you know the situation very well, don't you?

42
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,300
You should know very clearly

43
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:51,200
how much money our company lost because of this.

44
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:56,200
I understand. I'm here today to be face to face with you, just the two of us,

45
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,800
have an open and honest discussion.

46
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:01,000
I obviously didn't come today to evade responsibility.

47
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:04,100
I came to resolve the problem. If there's a problem, we should discuss it civilly.

48
00:04:06,100 --> 00:04:08,200
How do you want to resolve this then?

49
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:16,400
I do have an idea.

50
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,800
If...

51
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:24,000
If Mingyuan acquires Haiyao,

52
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:27,400
then we will be a family.

53
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:30,200
Since we are a family,

54
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:34,200
then the plagiarism issue shouldn't exist. Right?

55
00:04:39,180 --> 00:04:42,020
You'll be leaving in six days.

56
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,800
What do you want to do in these six days?

57
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:48,000
I haven't finished my assignment yet.

58
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,000
You still have to do an assignment?

59
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:53,000
You only have six days left yet you're not even thinking about how you're going to spend it with me?

60
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:56,600
I want to spend time with you, but I haven't finished my assignment.

61
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,600
What kind of assignment?

62
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:03,000
This time, I want to take some handmade ramie back to France.

63
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,600
Why do you suddenly want to find ramie?

64
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:08,600
Even though handmade ramie isn't that exquisite,

65
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:11,800
but it's very practical.

66
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:14,600
Compared to embroidery,

67
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:17,400
it also has a very long history.

68
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:21,600
Using it to present traditional culture is very suitable. What do you think?

69
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:24,000
Of course, I know a place that produces ramie.

70
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,100
Really?

71
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:27,700
Well... can you...

72
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:31,000
If you behave then I'll take you there.

73
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,600
Little Cutie.

74
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:45,000
President Tang, where are you going? I'll get a car to take you there.
[Ramie Processing Factory]

75
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:48,000
No need. We drove here.

76
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:53,800
Thank you very much for the lively lesson on ramie this time.

77
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:57,000
President Tang, you're too polite. This is what we should do.

78
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,300
- Have a safe trip.
- Thank you.

79
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:01,400
Thank you.

80
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,900
Let's go.

81
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:08,200
The ramie factory we visited is amazing.

82
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:11,400
Say, those ancient workers were so wise.

83
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:15,300
4,700 years ago, they already knew how to use ramie to make clothes.

84
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,800
Cutie, you've learned a lot.

85
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,320
I think I'll definitely get a good grade

86
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,500
on my assignment this time.

87
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,600
The scenery here is so nice.

88
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:33,000
If I knew you'd be so happy, should I have brought you here sooner?

89
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:36,000
Yes. Where are we going now?

90
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:43,400
Since we're already here, let's walk around.

91
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:47,200
I'm preparing to sell you in the deep mountain forest.

92
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,200
Right.

93
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:54,400
Say, can we rest for a while?

94
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:59,200
How long have we hiked? We've already rested three times.

95
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:02,700
I'm exhausted. How much longer do we need to keep climbing?

96
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,800
We are only halfway.

97
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,600
Halfway?

98
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:11,600
Based on your little physical strength, how can we reach the peak?

99
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:17,380
You usually don't exercise much so why aren't you exhausted?

100
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,400
I'm physically fit.

101
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,600
Let's go. Hang in there.

102
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,400
I'm very tired.

103
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:35,600
Sing a song for me. Let's sing while we walk, okay?

104
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,400
I advise you to not listen to me sing.

105
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:40,800
I heard from your brother you sing off-key, but I want to hear it.

106
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,700
- I'll sing for you then.
- All right.

107
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:47,300
♪  Descendants of the great mountains  ♪

108
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:51,000
What is it?

109
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,800
I twisted my ankle.

110
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,100
Come on.

111
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:58,400
♫ I really want to see your smile ♫

112
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:01,800
♫ Many people come and go ♫

113
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:05,400
♫ I want to be your last visitor ♫

114
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:09,000
♫ So please don't be afraid anymore ♫

115
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,800
It's swollen.

116
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:15,100
♫ Follow me in taking a huge step forward ♫

117
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:16,800
What are you doing?

118
00:08:19,110 --> 00:08:21,260
What are you looking for?

119
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:27,000
It's a good thing that I bought this with me.

120
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,400
Why do you have this...

121
00:08:31,130 --> 00:08:33,040
Endure it for a bit.

122
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:36,600
♫ When you feel tired, ♫

123
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,200
It stinks.

124
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,800
♫ I'll be your softest pillow ♫

125
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:43,600
♫ I want… ♫

126
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:48,200
What are we going to do now?

127
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:53,600
We still have to hike up there but I've twisted my ankle. How am I going to hike?

128
00:08:54,820 --> 00:08:56,700
I'll carry you.

129
00:08:57,800 --> 00:09:00,100
Don't carry me.

130
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:04,000
If I don't carry you, should I leave you here by yourself?

131
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,600
I can keep walking.

132
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,600
Say, you somehow twisted your ankle just by singing.

133
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:17,200
It's already difficult to hike up the mountain. It'll be more difficult if you carry me.

134
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:20,000
- What should we do then? Leave you here?
- I can keep going.

135
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,800
Come on. Stand up.

136
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:29,700
One, two, three! Let's go!

137
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:35,200
We are going up the mountain now. Continue singing.

138
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,400
What do you want to hear?

139
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:38,000
The Smurfs.

140
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,800
Listen carefully.

141
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:46,600
♪  On that mountainside of the sea there is a group of Smurfs  ♪

142
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,900
Are you Gargamel?

143
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:50,800
Am I heavy?

144
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:54,600
Old Tang, I found that not only did Fang Weiguo not stop what he was doing,

145
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:59,000
but he's also been making moves in the stock market lately.

146
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,800
What are you and Mingxuan thinking?

147
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:05,200
I am already feeling antsy and you're still here like this.

148
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:08,400
Tell me. What exactly are you thinking?

149
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:11,200
I can't possibly ignore this matter.

150
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,600
Old Xia, let me be honest with you.

151
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:16,000
Actually, I don't have that many funds

152
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:19,800
to buy stocks to contend with him.

153
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:23,000
If this continues,

154
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:26,500
we can only wait for the ten percent announcement.

155
00:10:27,230 --> 00:10:30,600
Lately, Mingxuan has also been busy out there

156
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,700
for this matter.

157
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:36,800
I also know very well that that there may not be any results for his efforts.

158
00:10:38,950 --> 00:10:42,060
Actually, I thought about it carefully.

159
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:43,950
I feel that in regards to this matter

160
00:10:43,950 --> 00:10:47,430
we are not at the end of the rope yet.

161
00:10:47,430 --> 00:10:51,170
I suddenly realized the key to solving this problem

162
00:10:51,170 --> 00:10:53,800
is Mingxuan's attitude.

163
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:57,470
Old Xia, since you have mentioned that,

164
00:10:57,470 --> 00:11:00,060
I believe you have your own take on this matter.

165
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:02,030
Tell me about it.

166
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,610
In regards to this matter...

167
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:24,680
I'm all right.

168
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,920
It's already swollen and you're saying you're all right?

169
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:31,220
- It doesn't hurt.
- It doesn't hurt?

170
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:37,430
Stop rubbing! Stop rubbing!

171
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,660
What are you thinking about?

172
00:11:51,970 --> 00:11:53,730
Before,

173
00:11:53,730 --> 00:11:57,400
I frequently thought of a sentence in the book, "The Little Prince."

174
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:02,220
"I live alone just like this,

175
00:12:03,410 --> 00:12:06,130
with no one whom I can truly talk to."

176
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:12,730
But ever since I met you,

177
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:17,080
I feel like I live every day very happily.

178
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:20,220
Life became colorful.

179
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:26,290
You are like my sleeping pill.

180
00:12:28,530 --> 00:12:31,160
Every night you help me sleep.

181
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:35,050
Every day I can have a good dream.

182
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:40,110
Thank you.

183
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,920
What's wrong?

184
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:01,550
I am thinking,

185
00:13:02,290 --> 00:13:04,410
should I stay and keep you company?

186
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:07,560
Absolutely.

187
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:12,200
Of course, you have to go back there to study well in school.

188
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,930
Don't you want to be an outstanding designer?

189
00:13:14,930 --> 00:13:17,400
I am waiting to see your fashion show.

190
00:13:25,770 --> 00:13:28,490
My future wife is the best.

191
00:13:39,700 --> 00:13:42,330
- I'm back.
- Hey, Zhu Zhu!

192
00:13:42,330 --> 00:13:44,450
- Have you eaten?
- I have.

193
00:13:44,450 --> 00:13:46,980
Come here. Have some fruit.

194
00:13:50,130 --> 00:13:52,100
The mango isn't bad.

195
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:56,680
It is really pretty. Where did you buy it from?

196
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:59,800
It is pretty, right? My friend gave it to me.

197
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:01,510
Very plump.

198
00:14:02,460 --> 00:14:06,150
A friend? Boy or girl?

199
00:14:06,150 --> 00:14:08,670
Why are you being so serious, Auntie?

200
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:12,730
You are a girl. Society is so messy. What would we do if you met a bad person?

201
00:14:12,730 --> 00:14:15,200
If you were to meet, what is it called? A playboy?

202
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:18,880
Playboy? Auntie, do you even know about playboys?

203
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:20,560
I am keeping up with the times.

204
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:23,630
That's easy to solve. Have Zhu Zhu get a boyfriend to protect her.

205
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:26,710
If you really have a boyfriend, you have to bring him home for us to see.

206
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:31,000
It is not a boyfriend. It is just a normal friend.

207
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,330
Do you dare to have a boyfriend?

208
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,810
Normal friend.

209
00:14:36,810 --> 00:14:38,560
Do you know where your brother went?

210
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:40,510
I have been calling him the whole day and can't get in touch with him.

211
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:43,640
It's probably because there's no signal in the mountains.

212
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:46,770
- Mountains?
- Why did he go to the mountains?

213
00:14:46,770 --> 00:14:48,550
He went to look for Sister Mo Fei.

214
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:51,710
Don't you feel that ever since he met Sister Mo Fei,

215
00:14:51,710 --> 00:14:53,640
he is much happier?

216
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:56,290
Even his life outside of work has become richer.

217
00:14:56,290 --> 00:14:58,650
Of course, it's a good thing for youngsters

218
00:14:58,650 --> 00:15:02,480
to use their free time to experience nature.

219
00:15:03,810 --> 00:15:05,720
What time is it right now?

220
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:08,230
How anxious is everyone over the company right now?

221
00:15:08,230 --> 00:15:10,850
Yet he's in the mood to go explore the mountains with her.

222
00:15:10,850 --> 00:15:15,000
If Xia Zhendong and the other shareholders find out, what would they think?

223
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,590
Isn't there a saying?

224
00:15:16,590 --> 00:15:19,350
"Only people who know how to play know how to work."

225
00:15:19,350 --> 00:15:21,800
He should have his freedom.

226
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:23,370
He is the company's president.

227
00:15:23,370 --> 00:15:27,280
His freedom and non-freedom are related to the company's interests.

228
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:28,920
If he wants freedom, fine.

229
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:32,560
The unemployed wanderers of the street are very free. Will he go become them?

230
00:15:34,570 --> 00:15:37,610
I can't win against you. You are always right.

231
00:15:41,610 --> 00:15:44,970
Oh my! Be careful, be careful.

232
00:15:50,090 --> 00:15:51,200
- Mom.
- It's swollen!

233
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:54,030
I'm fine. I'm fine.

234
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:56,910
- It doesn't hurt at all!
- I'm sorry. I didn't take good care of her, Aunt.

235
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:59,180
How is it your fault? It's hers.

236
00:15:59,180 --> 00:16:02,020
Always running around.

237
00:16:02,020 --> 00:16:04,600
I'm not a child. I can take good care of myself.

238
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:06,830
Children are more sensible than you, all right?

239
00:16:06,830 --> 00:16:09,700
You don't even think to tell us that you are going so far. If it weren't for Brother-in-Law, would you have been able to come back?

240
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:12,060
Let me warn you. Don't think that because my foot is twisted that I can't beat you!

241
00:16:12,060 --> 00:16:13,730
Enough!

242
00:16:13,730 --> 00:16:16,370
Forget the fact that you two argue when you're home alone. You two are still arguing with a guest here?

243
00:16:16,370 --> 00:16:19,240
I'm already used to them being like this, Aunt.

244
00:16:20,160 --> 00:16:22,790
Mingxuan, there's no time like the present.

245
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:25,740
I was just talking to Mo Fan about inviting you here for dinner.

246
00:16:25,740 --> 00:16:29,300
- Since you have come today, stay for dinner.
- Okay.

247
00:16:29,300 --> 00:16:32,790
Then have a seat for now. Keep the ice on.

248
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:38,360
- Mom, I'll help you.
- I'm fine.

249
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:41,490
- Thank you.
- You are still saying you're all right? You even cried in the car earlier.

250
00:16:41,490 --> 00:16:44,600
Isn't it embarrassing? Who was crying

251
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:47,430
- saying "it hurts"?
- Stop talking about it.

252
00:16:55,580 --> 00:16:59,990
Mingxuan, we called you here because of this.

253
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:02,580
Earlier your Uncle Xia came.

254
00:17:02,580 --> 00:17:07,140
He came to discuss the shares between our two families.

255
00:17:07,140 --> 00:17:11,320
It is like this. The Xia family will continue to support us as always.

256
00:17:11,320 --> 00:17:14,890
Currently, the Xia family's shares are in Xueling's control.

257
00:17:14,890 --> 00:17:18,040
He suggested that we act in concert.

258
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:20,480
If that's the case, with our families' strength,

259
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:23,390
as well as those of some small shareholders who support us,

260
00:17:23,390 --> 00:17:27,390
then Fang Weiguo's side won't be a threat at all. Isn't that right?

261
00:17:27,390 --> 00:17:28,830
Yes.

262
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:35,560
From my understanding of Uncle Xia,

263
00:17:36,100 --> 00:17:38,520
- there should be more, right?
- Yes.

264
00:17:39,590 --> 00:17:42,540
How should I say this? Uncle Xia's suggestion is

265
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:46,380
since the two families' shares are combined

266
00:17:46,380 --> 00:17:48,690
towards Xueling,

267
00:17:48,690 --> 00:17:51,680
we should give her some...

268
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:58,210
Reassurance... a simple reassurance. Reassurance.

269
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,660
What reassurance?

270
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:03,740
Why are you making it sound like a deal?

271
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:05,450
You say it then.

272
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,800
Son, it is like this.

273
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:11,290
We have watched Xueling grow up so we know her extremely well.

274
00:18:11,290 --> 00:18:14,420
You two have also been childhood sweethearts for so many years,

275
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:16,000
so there should be feelings.

276
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:19,200
The Xia family also isn't willing to contribute for nothing.

277
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:23,300
The shares were originally Xia Zhendong's wedding dowry for Xueling.

278
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:26,120
I feel that makes perfect sense.

279
00:18:26,120 --> 00:18:30,190
So... that is the current situation.

280
00:18:30,190 --> 00:18:34,370
We also cannot tie up a white wolf with our bare hands, right?

281
00:18:36,430 --> 00:18:39,020
Actually, you guys don't need to say this much nor need to beat around the bush.

282
00:18:39,020 --> 00:18:42,470
For the company's interest, you two are prepared to sell your son again.

283
00:18:42,470 --> 00:18:44,340
- Is that right?
- No.

284
00:18:44,340 --> 00:18:48,390
Let me tell you two this. Impossible.

285
00:18:48,390 --> 00:18:52,160
- Mingxuan!
- It is not my idea!

286
00:18:53,010 --> 00:18:54,950
I knew we wouldn't be able to persuade him.

287
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:57,990
B-But we have to solve this matter. Do you have another plan?

288
00:18:57,990 --> 00:18:59,970
I don't have another plan but

289
00:18:59,970 --> 00:19:03,320
Old Xia is really something. Why would he mention this?

290
00:19:03,320 --> 00:19:05,680
Why is this child like this?

291
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:07,940
Is he not a part of this family?

292
00:19:07,940 --> 00:19:10,930
Is he not the person who benefits most from the company?

293
00:19:10,930 --> 00:19:13,290
Right now, the family and the company are in a crisis,

294
00:19:13,290 --> 00:19:16,650
- so what if he makes some sacrifices?
- It is not the same.

295
00:19:16,650 --> 00:19:19,050
- How is it not the same?
- You and Old Xia are talking about interest,

296
00:19:19,050 --> 00:19:21,520
but he is talking about his feelings.

297
00:19:21,520 --> 00:19:26,220
Right? We should respect his wishes.

298
00:19:26,220 --> 00:19:29,190
He can't just enjoy the benefits of the company

299
00:19:29,190 --> 00:19:31,760
and not be willing to make any sacrifices, right?

300
00:19:31,760 --> 00:19:34,980
The company is so big. Who hasn't made any sacrifices?

301
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:40,660
Let's think of something else.

302
00:19:47,070 --> 00:19:50,760
What? Why do you keep on moving around in bed?

303
00:19:53,790 --> 00:19:56,400
- What's wrong?
- Today, when Mingxuan

304
00:19:56,400 --> 00:20:00,650
was talking to me with that attitude, why didn't you say a single thing?

305
00:20:00,650 --> 00:20:02,690
What do you want me to say?

306
00:20:02,690 --> 00:20:06,520
I cannot force him to marry a certain woman.

307
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:08,170
You also cannot.

308
00:20:08,170 --> 00:20:12,400
Besides, should we have learned our lesson from our experience with Fang Qian?

309
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:14,380
If you keep on pushing him

310
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:17,800
and one day your son decides to be a bachelor for the rest of his life because you pushed him too far, let's see what you'll do.

311
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:20,080
You will regret it for life.

312
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:25,890
Let me ask you.

313
00:20:25,890 --> 00:20:29,480
When we were young, I wished that you would spend more time with me.

314
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:33,130
Remember my birthday, remember our anniversary date.

315
00:20:33,130 --> 00:20:34,880
Did you remember them?

316
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:39,050
- Those aren't important.
- They are. You don't even remember them now.

317
00:20:39,050 --> 00:20:41,340
When Mingxuan was 7,

318
00:20:41,340 --> 00:20:43,040
he had a high fever and pneumonia.

319
00:20:43,040 --> 00:20:45,620
You were at the factory rushing to produce the products with the workers.

320
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:47,180
You didn't come home all night.

321
00:20:47,180 --> 00:20:50,080
I took him to the hospital alone.

322
00:20:50,080 --> 00:20:53,160
That year, I also had kidney stone removal surgery.

323
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:56,010
I signed the papers alone and got the surgery alone.

324
00:20:56,010 --> 00:20:59,330
Where were you? You were on a business trip overseas.

325
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:01,800
Yes. Wasn't I busy?

326
00:21:01,800 --> 00:21:05,020
That's right. Who hasn't made sacrifices for this company

327
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:09,000
to get as big as it is today?

328
00:21:09,660 --> 00:21:12,840
Your position dictates what you should be saying.

329
00:21:12,840 --> 00:21:15,120
Today, he only cares about those trivial romantic feelings.

330
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:17,430
How can he achieve great deeds?

331
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:20,200
Ever since ancient times, even emperors had to make decisions.

332
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:23,820
Why can't he make sacrifices for the company's interests?

333
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:26,640
Unless he can take care of both things,

334
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:28,970
not only take care of them but take care of them well,

335
00:21:28,970 --> 00:21:31,240
then I will shut up forever.

336
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,410
Don't pretend you can't hear me.

337
00:21:39,310 --> 00:21:41,440
You just indulge him.

338
00:21:42,030 --> 00:21:43,900
You've spoiled him, causing him to be like this.

339
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:56,600
[Shanghai Delta Health Hosptial]

340
00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:59,310
I told you I'm fine but you insist on making me come here.

341
00:21:59,310 --> 00:22:01,000
Do you have that much free time?

342
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:04,920
Do you think I want to do this? Your man gave me this task.

343
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:08,030
He said that when he's not around, I have to take good care of you.

344
00:22:08,030 --> 00:22:10,090
I realized, in his eyes, you

345
00:22:10,090 --> 00:22:12,790
can't take care of yourself at all.

346
00:22:12,790 --> 00:22:15,660
Say, when did he buy you over?

347
00:22:15,660 --> 00:22:18,080
Actually, I sometimes don't get it.

348
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:21,840
How did President Tang come to like you?

349
00:22:26,760 --> 00:22:28,880
What are you saying?

350
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:31,600
I, your sister, am outstanding.

351
00:22:44,190 --> 00:22:46,850
This doesn't say what floor.

352
00:22:55,270 --> 00:22:56,880
Hello.

353
00:22:57,450 --> 00:22:59,790
Hello, Xueling.

354
00:23:00,560 --> 00:23:02,160
Hello.

355
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:05,180
Can you hear me?

356
00:23:05,180 --> 00:23:06,810
Xueling?

357
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:12,160
I'm sorry, hi.

358
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:14,580
I want to ask...

359
00:23:17,990 --> 00:23:20,610
We've met somewhere before, right?

360
00:23:20,610 --> 00:23:23,760
I also think you look very familiar, too.

361
00:23:25,930 --> 00:23:27,640
Why do you look so familiar?

362
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:29,250
Is your husband Tang Qiren?

363
00:23:29,250 --> 00:23:31,210
That's right.

364
00:23:31,210 --> 00:23:34,120
You're Mo Yuxin. You modeled for our company before.

365
00:23:34,120 --> 00:23:36,170
Oh my heavens. It was so long ago and you still remember?

366
00:23:36,170 --> 00:23:38,640
Oh my heavens. Let me give you a hug.

367
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:40,140
How come you haven't changed a bit?

368
00:23:40,140 --> 00:23:42,190
- You're still so beautiful.
- Oh, no. No, no.

369
00:23:42,190 --> 00:23:44,560
- Do you live here?
- Yes.

370
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:47,130
Look at us, just chatting. Come up to my home to sit.

371
00:23:47,130 --> 00:23:48,820
- What a coincidence.
- Let's go. Let's go.

372
00:23:48,820 --> 00:23:51,020
How did I run into you here?

373
00:23:51,020 --> 00:23:53,300
What a coincidence.

374
00:23:53,300 --> 00:23:54,930
It has been years since we last met each other.

375
00:23:54,930 --> 00:23:57,510
I never expected us to run into each other in the hallway.

376
00:23:57,510 --> 00:23:59,730
Yes. This is probably fate.

377
00:23:59,730 --> 00:24:03,760
You don't say. You are getting more and more elegant over the years.

378
00:24:03,760 --> 00:24:06,770
No, no. I'm old now. You're the one who hasn't changed.

379
00:24:06,770 --> 00:24:09,490
I remember when you worked with us.

380
00:24:09,490 --> 00:24:12,280
You were the best model on the team.

381
00:24:12,280 --> 00:24:14,810
Have you switched careers now?

382
00:24:14,810 --> 00:24:16,260
Switched careers? No.

383
00:24:16,260 --> 00:24:19,680
I noticed there is a lot of tailor-related stuff here.

384
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:22,210
They belong to my daughter.

385
00:24:22,210 --> 00:24:23,570
Oh right, I remember now.

386
00:24:23,570 --> 00:24:25,180
- You have a son and a daughter.
- That's right.

387
00:24:25,180 --> 00:24:26,850
Is your daughter married yet?

388
00:24:26,850 --> 00:24:29,880
Her? She is still a student.

389
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:31,670
- Where is she going to university?
- In France.

390
00:24:31,670 --> 00:24:32,990
France? What does she study?

391
00:24:32,990 --> 00:24:34,010
Fashion design.

392
00:24:34,010 --> 00:24:37,590
Look, she is inheriting your business. That's so great.

393
00:24:37,590 --> 00:24:39,480
Even so, she worries me.

394
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:42,320
What about you? I heard that you have an excellent son.

395
00:24:42,320 --> 00:24:45,350
Of course. Like his father, when it comes to work,

396
00:24:45,350 --> 00:24:48,300
he's a workaholic and never home.

397
00:24:48,300 --> 00:24:51,210
However, his love life makes me so worried.

398
00:24:51,210 --> 00:24:52,700
Why?

399
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:55,070
My husband and I think this one girl suits him.

400
00:24:55,070 --> 00:24:57,610
Her family background matches ours.

401
00:24:57,610 --> 00:25:00,930
They also grew up together and are childhood sweethearts.

402
00:25:00,930 --> 00:25:02,500
They've known each other for almost 30 years.

403
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:03,600
That sounds good.

404
00:25:03,600 --> 00:25:05,380
And they have always gotten along.

405
00:25:05,380 --> 00:25:08,480
That girl is talented and beautiful.

406
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:11,660
If my son marries her, then it's a blessing for our family.

407
00:25:11,660 --> 00:25:14,930
We don't know how but a temptress has appeared lately

408
00:25:14,930 --> 00:25:18,290
and caused my son to be delirious.

409
00:25:18,290 --> 00:25:21,460
We really don't have a say in our children's love lives these days.

410
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:22,960
He won't listen at all.

411
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:25,550
If I comment on it, he'll say he has a headache and leave.

412
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:29,070
There is nothing I can do. I'm so worried.

413
00:25:30,990 --> 00:25:33,000
Is that your family photo?

414
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:35,480
- Yes.
- Let me see.

415
00:25:36,150 --> 00:25:38,380
They must be so pretty.

416
00:25:38,380 --> 00:25:42,290
This is my son, Mo Fan, and this is my daughter.

417
00:25:46,050 --> 00:25:48,460
Mo Fei is your daughter?

418
00:25:48,460 --> 00:25:51,850
Yes. Have you seen her before?

419
00:25:51,850 --> 00:25:54,330
I'm Tang Mingxuan's mom.

420
00:25:54,330 --> 00:25:56,720
She is the temptress I was talking about.

421
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,910
- Watch what you say.
- That's exactly how I'm going to speak.

422
00:25:58,910 --> 00:26:01,090
- Who are you calling a temptress?
- Your daughter.

423
00:26:01,090 --> 00:26:03,110
Doesn't ruining others' relationships make her a temptress?

424
00:26:03,110 --> 00:26:04,600
How can the dignified wife of Chairman Tang speak...

425
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:06,830
- Is our mom fighting with someone?
- ...so rudely?

426
00:26:06,830 --> 00:26:08,240
- She must be watching TV.
- I'm rude?

427
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,630
You are classy yet the daughter you raised

428
00:26:09,630 --> 00:26:10,890
ruins other people's relationships.

429
00:26:10,890 --> 00:26:13,060
I understand now.

430
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:17,320
If I had known Tang Mingxuan's mom was so rude,

431
00:26:17,320 --> 00:26:18,630
I would be against them being together.

432
00:26:18,630 --> 00:26:20,660
You are against it?

433
00:26:21,270 --> 00:26:23,900
I should be the one who's against it!

434
00:26:23,900 --> 00:26:26,590
- What's wrong?
- I have never met...

435
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:28,710
Auntie? What are you doing here?

436
00:26:28,710 --> 00:26:31,290
You are back just in time. I came here today to see you.

437
00:26:31,290 --> 00:26:33,960
Please stay away from Tang Mingxuan.

438
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:35,150
Stop bothering him.

439
00:26:35,150 --> 00:26:36,550
Please leave my home.

440
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:38,670
I will leave after I finish.

441
00:26:38,670 --> 00:26:41,830
I respect you, Auntie, and I hope you can respect my family.

442
00:26:41,830 --> 00:26:43,720
This has nothing to do with them.

443
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:45,620
Please do not come to bother them.

444
00:26:45,620 --> 00:26:48,870
We can talk elsewhere. You can decide when and where.

445
00:26:48,870 --> 00:26:50,640
I'll wait for your call.

446
00:26:54,030 --> 00:26:55,650
Teach your daughter to be upright.

447
00:26:55,650 --> 00:26:57,820
Rude.

448
00:27:01,990 --> 00:27:04,440
[Yan Xu: Missed phone calls]

449
00:27:09,740 --> 00:27:10,830
Are you asleep?

450
00:27:10,830 --> 00:27:12,880
I'm not, Dad.

451
00:27:16,330 --> 00:27:18,950
I noticed that your light is still on.

452
00:27:18,950 --> 00:27:21,750
So I came to talk to you.

453
00:27:27,720 --> 00:27:32,400
I... went to the Tang house a few days ago.

454
00:27:36,820 --> 00:27:40,380
Don't you want to know why I went there?

455
00:27:40,380 --> 00:27:43,250
Don't you go there often?

456
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:52,500
Child, tell me the truth.

457
00:27:52,500 --> 00:27:55,460
Your relationship with Tang Mingxuan...

458
00:27:56,470 --> 00:27:58,880
What are your thoughts?

459
00:28:00,390 --> 00:28:04,980
Haven't I told you before? We were not meant to be.

460
00:28:07,460 --> 00:28:11,750
Then aren't all your efforts and persistence in the past for nothing?

461
00:28:17,150 --> 00:28:22,570
Sometimes, the success and happiness we pursue

462
00:28:23,500 --> 00:28:25,440
seem very far away,

463
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:28,980
but in fact, are just a tiny step away from us.

464
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:34,490
You will get them with just this little bit more persistence.

465
00:28:40,180 --> 00:28:43,170
Your Uncle and Auntie Tang both said

466
00:28:43,810 --> 00:28:46,360
they support you on this matter.

467
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:51,240
They are willing to try to convince Mingxuan. What do you think?

468
00:28:52,620 --> 00:28:56,530
I used to think marrying him

469
00:28:56,530 --> 00:28:59,770
would be the happiest thing in my life.

470
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:04,130
I tried so hard and put in so much effort

471
00:29:04,130 --> 00:29:06,440
because I believed

472
00:29:06,440 --> 00:29:09,520
one day, he would notice how good I was to him.

473
00:29:09,520 --> 00:29:14,790
I would then wear a wedding gown and stand by his side.

474
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:22,550
But after all that happened,

475
00:29:22,550 --> 00:29:24,890
I feel that I may have been wrong.

476
00:29:32,380 --> 00:29:34,040
Thanks.

477
00:29:34,730 --> 00:29:38,920
Child, thanks for telling me that.

478
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:44,180
Actually, I have reflected on myself these days, too.

479
00:29:44,180 --> 00:29:49,530
Insisting on this matter, do I want to give my daughter happiness

480
00:29:49,530 --> 00:29:53,620
or would I just be pushing her into a fire pit? I really had no idea.

481
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:57,560
I really had no idea.

482
00:30:00,090 --> 00:30:05,210
Dad, do you think I will be happy with him?

483
00:30:13,290 --> 00:30:15,850
I laid it all out to your Uncle Tang.

484
00:30:15,850 --> 00:30:18,070
I only have one daughter.

485
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:21,560
I hope you will be happy.

486
00:30:21,560 --> 00:30:23,750
If you two can be together, then great.

487
00:30:23,750 --> 00:30:27,450
But if you can't,

488
00:30:28,410 --> 00:30:33,020
I can't help the Tang family this time.

489
00:30:36,020 --> 00:30:37,640
Go to bed.

490
00:30:59,760 --> 00:31:03,060
Can you stop following me like a spirit?

491
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:05,080
I'm just worried about you. What if something bad happens?

492
00:31:05,080 --> 00:31:07,440
What can happen? What is there for you to be worried about?

493
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:09,130
No, I must escort you here.

494
00:31:09,130 --> 00:31:11,720
Fine, I'm here now. You can leave.

495
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:13,840
No, let me walk you in.

496
00:31:18,970 --> 00:31:20,640
Hello, Auntie.

497
00:31:22,770 --> 00:31:26,020
What is this? Both sister and brother have come.

498
00:31:26,020 --> 00:31:28,230
Is this a show of force?

499
00:31:33,090 --> 00:31:34,360
What are you doing?

500
00:31:34,360 --> 00:31:37,860
All right. Don't get angry with her in a bit. Have a good chat, you hear me?

501
00:31:38,620 --> 00:31:41,410
Whose side are you on?

502
00:31:41,410 --> 00:31:42,920
Get lost!

503
00:31:54,820 --> 00:31:59,830
Miss Mo, our last meeting was very unpleasant.

504
00:31:59,830 --> 00:32:01,970
I can't guarantee this time

505
00:32:01,970 --> 00:32:04,290
will be a pleasant one, either.

506
00:32:04,290 --> 00:32:07,020
So I'll be straightforward.

507
00:32:07,020 --> 00:32:10,410
You and Mingxuan are from two different worlds.

508
00:32:10,990 --> 00:32:14,780
Even if you two are together now, you can't make it in the long run.

509
00:32:15,690 --> 00:32:18,340
You know what Mingxuan has.

510
00:32:18,340 --> 00:32:21,250
Even if he wastes several years on you,

511
00:32:21,250 --> 00:32:23,530
he can afford it.

512
00:32:24,130 --> 00:32:27,750
But you're not the same. You're a girl.

513
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:30,350
You need to get married in the coming several years.

514
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:33,440
If you miss the window, your value will decrease.

515
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:35,690
Then it will be hard for you

516
00:32:35,690 --> 00:32:37,820
to find a good man for yourself.

517
00:32:37,820 --> 00:32:40,060
Although what I've said is hard to hear,

518
00:32:40,060 --> 00:32:42,540
that's the reality of things.

519
00:32:42,540 --> 00:32:44,160
Since you're so smart,

520
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:46,720
you should understand my meaning.

521
00:32:49,550 --> 00:32:53,180
Auntie, is this all you wanted to say?

522
00:32:53,180 --> 00:32:57,090
Of course, if you can promise me one thing,

523
00:32:57,090 --> 00:32:59,110
that would be great.

524
00:32:59,110 --> 00:33:02,750
Promise that you will not pester him ever again.

525
00:33:02,750 --> 00:33:05,000
Tell me your conditions.

526
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:07,960
I will try my best to make them happen.

527
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:11,500
If you insist on marrying a man from a wealthy family,

528
00:33:11,500 --> 00:33:14,100
I can introduce you to other resources.

529
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:18,280
I know so many wealthy young men.

530
00:33:28,190 --> 00:33:31,360
I admit that Mingxuan is outstanding.

531
00:33:31,360 --> 00:33:33,260
I love him very much, too.

532
00:33:33,260 --> 00:33:36,530
Plus, I admire him from the bottom of my heart.

533
00:33:36,530 --> 00:33:40,950
I'm honored he would be with me.

534
00:33:40,950 --> 00:33:43,930
But if one day he wants to leave me,

535
00:33:43,930 --> 00:33:46,840
I won't make a scene, either.

536
00:33:46,840 --> 00:33:51,090
I have a clear plan for my future.

537
00:33:51,090 --> 00:33:55,320
Whether we continue together or separately,

538
00:33:55,320 --> 00:33:59,630
I think that is our own business.

539
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:04,240
Besides, no one can predict the future.

540
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:06,080
Isn't that right?

541
00:34:10,190 --> 00:34:13,140
Auntie, if you...

542
00:34:13,140 --> 00:34:16,200
want me to promise you something today,

543
00:34:17,010 --> 00:34:20,540
then I'm so sorry to have to disappoint you.

544
00:34:21,270 --> 00:34:25,130
I'm not sure what the point of this promise is.

545
00:34:25,130 --> 00:34:28,850
Firstly, it is not legally binding.

546
00:34:28,850 --> 00:34:33,390
Secondly, I don't think it has any control over anything.

547
00:34:33,390 --> 00:34:36,370
Besides, on what grounds would this promise be built on?

548
00:34:36,370 --> 00:34:39,730
Why should I make a promise to you rather than you to me?

549
00:34:39,730 --> 00:34:44,440
I'll admit you are my elder so I should respect you.

550
00:34:45,450 --> 00:34:49,730
But... since we are both human,

551
00:34:49,730 --> 00:34:51,960
aren't we equal?

552
00:34:56,070 --> 00:35:00,890
Of course, I won't make your trip here a waste.

553
00:35:00,890 --> 00:35:03,610
I can tell you very clearly

554
00:35:03,610 --> 00:35:06,540
I'm still a student now

555
00:35:06,540 --> 00:35:09,080
so I will leave Shanghai soon.

556
00:35:09,610 --> 00:35:15,120
I'm not sure if the distance will become an obstacle in our relationship.

557
00:35:15,120 --> 00:35:18,430
However, I can be sure

558
00:35:18,430 --> 00:35:20,990
that it will lessen the times your son sees me.

559
00:35:21,750 --> 00:35:25,650
I made this decision, not because of pressure from you,

560
00:35:25,650 --> 00:35:28,490
but to be responsible for my own future.

561
00:35:32,390 --> 00:35:37,360
No one can force me to be with anybody.

562
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:40,390
So I won't separate from Mingxuan

563
00:35:40,390 --> 00:35:42,860
because of someone's pressure.

564
00:35:53,560 --> 00:35:55,830
Dad.

565
00:35:55,830 --> 00:35:59,740
Do you know that our stock price keeps rising?

566
00:35:59,740 --> 00:36:01,960
Fang Weiguo has made an announcement.

567
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:04,730
He now has 10% of our shares.

568
00:36:04,730 --> 00:36:07,280
As long as our stock price continues to rise,

569
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,680
he won't be able to acquire more.

570
00:36:09,680 --> 00:36:12,180
If Xueling marries into our family,

571
00:36:12,180 --> 00:36:16,220
things you are worrying about will be solved automatically.

572
00:36:16,220 --> 00:36:19,920
Our Mingxuan is bewitched by that girl

573
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:22,320
so he rejected Xueling.

574
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:29,770
Mom.

575
00:36:30,730 --> 00:36:32,710
Sit down.

576
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:36,390
- I haven't finished yet and you're leaving.
- My apologies.

577
00:36:45,180 --> 00:36:48,560
In regards to this matter,

578
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:51,250
I want to say something fair.

579
00:36:51,250 --> 00:36:53,660
He and Xueling have known each other for so many years.

580
00:36:53,660 --> 00:36:57,920
If the children really had feelings for each other, would they have waited until now?

581
00:36:58,430 --> 00:37:01,160
Also, if you have the child sacrifice his happiness and relationship

582
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:05,130
for the interests of the company, then, as his parents,

583
00:37:05,130 --> 00:37:08,430
aren't we too selfish? That's not appropriate.

584
00:37:09,300 --> 00:37:12,000
Do you have a faster or better solution for this matter then?

585
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,800
- Of course not.
- Exactly.

586
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:17,810
Then should we just watch Fang Weiguo take over our Mingyuan?

587
00:37:17,810 --> 00:37:22,190
He is young so he can easily be affected by his emotions. What about you?

588
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:25,320
Love and career, aren't you aware of which is more important?

589
00:37:25,930 --> 00:37:28,990
Okay, okay. I'll go upstairs to reflect on myself.

590
00:37:28,990 --> 00:37:32,260
You sit down as well. I haven't finished talking yet.

591
00:37:38,230 --> 00:37:41,360
I'm not afraid of you knowing. I went to see Mo Fei.

592
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:43,120
What?

593
00:37:48,090 --> 00:37:51,020
Why did you go to her? This is our family's issue.

594
00:37:51,020 --> 00:37:54,780
That girl told me clearly that her priority

595
00:37:54,780 --> 00:37:56,480
is to go abroad to study.

596
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:59,320
No matter what, she won't stay in China.

597
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:02,210
She is young but ambitious.

598
00:38:02,660 --> 00:38:06,080
She is not someone to settle down with.

599
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,590
Xueling is different though.

600
00:38:08,590 --> 00:38:10,940
Over the years, she has been

601
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:13,020
the same towards you and our family.

602
00:38:13,020 --> 00:38:15,820
She has wholeheartedly devoted herself to you.

603
00:38:15,820 --> 00:38:19,550
You won't choose such a good girl. Instead, you insist on choosing that Mo Fei?

604
00:38:19,550 --> 00:38:22,830
You are not young anymore. Being in charge of such a big company,

605
00:38:22,830 --> 00:38:24,540
are you aware of

606
00:38:24,540 --> 00:38:26,340
what is more important?

607
00:38:26,340 --> 00:38:29,830
I will take care of work properly. However, when it comes to my personal relationships,

608
00:38:29,830 --> 00:38:32,120
