609
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:33,840
I'm your mom, not your employee.

610
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:36,600
Mind your attitude when you speak.

611
00:38:37,990 --> 00:38:41,640
Fine. If you think that I do not fulfill

612
00:38:41,640 --> 00:38:43,540
my work duties well, then I'll resign.

613
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:47,900
I respect your suggestions for my love life. You can make your suggstions.

614
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:50,770
But I have the right to make my own decisions. Okay, Mom?

615
00:38:50,770 --> 00:38:53,760
Stop going to see her. Why are you seeing her?

616
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:55,670
It's your son who pestered her and wants to be with her.

617
00:38:55,670 --> 00:38:58,720
Whether she'll choose to be with me, in the end, is another matter.

618
00:38:58,720 --> 00:39:03,020
Stop thinking you are above everyone.

619
00:39:03,020 --> 00:39:04,960
That makes sense.

620
00:39:11,190 --> 00:39:14,750
You just wait and regret it when Mingyuan is no longer ours.

621
00:39:21,990 --> 00:39:23,800
I will go wash some grapes for my mom.

622
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:25,460
You should.

623
00:39:27,670 --> 00:39:29,820
Thanks.

